        %span.font-black
          TRAILBLAZER PRO
        %br{ class: "lg:hidden" }
        in action
      %p.section-description.text-white.text-lg{ class: "text-xl" }
        Benefit from
        %b TRAILBLAZER PRO
        features that speed up your code development
        %br.hidden{ class: "lg:inline" }
        by simplified code snippets.
      .flex.flex-col.mt-16.text-center{ class: "md:text-left md:flex-row md:gap-16 lg:gap-20
